{"tid":1929311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国長征七號改中型運載火箭發射任務失敗","createTime":"2020-03-17T00:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T05:25:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"31db6372be0b7374cc3b1b9a318e68aacb66f24f","tid":1929311,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:56:01.000Z","msg":"新華社報導，16日晚間9時34分，中國在海南文昌航太發射場進行長征七號改中型運載火箭首次飛行任務，火箭飛行出現異常，發射任務失利。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，後續將集合專家對故障原因進行調查分析。此前媒體報導，此次發射的是長征七號改（長征七號A），是在原有長征七號二級火箭的基礎上、加上第三級，第三級火箭採用液氫液氧發動機，火箭高度也增加至60公尺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/ait/202003170031.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fait%2F202003170031.aspx&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8D2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=4911ed40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/ait/202003170031.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"96a612a490957f5756c1614c6425fd82eebb1549","tid":1929311,"uid":522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:58:05.000Z","msg":"整舊屎出黎篤眼篤鼻"},{"pid":"e7d164ec27807b2482acd074a2aaa8274c926000","tid":1929311,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:59:09.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"9640c97c3d3d7b722922d47573f59a553fae3cd6","tid":1929311,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:00:46.000Z","msg":"多難興邦"},{"pid":"aa73bb9cd74c46f1cefa6ec3a7c76cd83f3d0bb8","tid":1929311,"uid":209644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:01:30.000Z","msg":"支那做假"},{"pid":"c66f037400e7e4106a111575ce6c2ef2d29b6df1","tid":1929311,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:02:15.000Z","msg":"有冇爆炸片睇？"},{"pid":"10e6db94d2c8e70c98d63b2f905c574f36b5a433","tid":1929311,"uid":44454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:09:58.000Z","msg":"維尼:便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「異常不能算失敗&hellip;&hellip;異常！&hellip;&hellip;中國人的事，能算輸麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「 寬衣通商，什